content:
Plan Automations Based on Start-Time Scheduling Recommendations

Automation Studio experiences significant traffic during the beginning of the hour (:00) and middle (:30). Use start-time scheduling recommendations to help you plan automation start times and distribute tasks to more efficient periods. Existing automation schedules are unaffected, and you can continue to specify the exact start time.

Where: This change applies to all Marketing Cloud Engagement editions.

When: This feature is available on a rolling basis starting in June 2024.
